<h3>Building Global Brand Name Recognition</h3>

<p>On May 14, 1997, Parent Company of global logistics provider
Circle International changed its name from The Harper Group to
Circle International Group and NASDAQ trading symbol from HARG to
CRCL. This reflects the Company's corporate strategy worldwide to
unify its more than 350 offices under the Circle International
identity. </p>

<p><a href="namechange.htm">Name Change Press Release</a> </p>

